  "detailed_description": "Star Devil is a Sci-fi Station Survival Roguelike Game with dynamic alien infection.<br>Playable in both single-player and split-screen co-op.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/eafaaf21bba9ae32e856bbdd85469a86.avif?t=1670005419\" width=640 height=128 /></span><br><br>In Star Devil you will try to escape an increasingly alien infected space station.<br>To escape you will need to pass through the various different levels of the space station.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast and Deadly combat</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/39690a9a6214cb0c0444528edd1290a1.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/39690a9a6214cb0c0444528edd1290a1.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/39690a9a6214cb0c0444528edd1290a1.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You need to master your weapons and stay focused.<br>Because one hit can mean your doom, so keep moving.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural generated space station</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/e06f24c2b4f2c950ff1c4d3ea7ddcd22.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/e06f24c2b4f2c950ff1c4d3ea7ddcd22.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/e06f24c2b4f2c950ff1c4d3ea7ddcd22.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Procedurally generated space station to keep each playthrough fresh.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic alien infestation</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/02c71521f4abdd28503d26cfcee37351.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/02c71521f4abdd28503d26cfcee37351.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/02c71521f4abdd28503d26cfcee37351.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Escaping the space station is not an easy feat. The space station will get more and more infected by the aliens the longer you spend roaming it.<br>You can counter this by eliminating the aliens and their eggs to slow down the infestation.<br><br>But you can only slow down the infestation, not stop it. So be swift because otherwise the aliens will corner you fast.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single-player or Split-screen Co-Op</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/98e8c59cc7431eb0d3cb8f161271ab17.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/98e8c59cc7431eb0d3cb8f161271ab17.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/98e8c59cc7431eb0d3cb8f161271ab17.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Playable in both single-player and split-screen co-op.<br><strong>You need at least one controller to play split-screen co-op.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "Star Devil is a Sci-fi Station Survival Roguelike Game with dynamic alien infection.<br>Playable in both single-player and split-screen co-op.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/eafaaf21bba9ae32e856bbdd85469a86.avif?t=1670005419\" width=640 height=128 /></span><br><br>In Star Devil you will try to escape an increasingly alien infected space station.<br>To escape you will need to pass through the various different levels of the space station.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fast and Deadly combat</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/39690a9a6214cb0c0444528edd1290a1.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/39690a9a6214cb0c0444528edd1290a1.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/39690a9a6214cb0c0444528edd1290a1.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You need to master your weapons and stay focused.<br>Because one hit can mean your doom, so keep moving.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural generated space station</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/e06f24c2b4f2c950ff1c4d3ea7ddcd22.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/e06f24c2b4f2c950ff1c4d3ea7ddcd22.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/e06f24c2b4f2c950ff1c4d3ea7ddcd22.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Procedurally generated space station to keep each playthrough fresh.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic alien infestation</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/02c71521f4abdd28503d26cfcee37351.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/02c71521f4abdd28503d26cfcee37351.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/02c71521f4abdd28503d26cfcee37351.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Escaping the space station is not an easy feat. The space station will get more and more infected by the aliens the longer you spend roaming it.<br>You can counter this by eliminating the aliens and their eggs to slow down the infestation.<br><br>But you can only slow down the infestation, not stop it. So be swift because otherwise the aliens will corner you fast.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Single-player or Split-screen Co-Op</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/98e8c59cc7431eb0d3cb8f161271ab17.poster.avif?t=1670005419\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/98e8c59cc7431eb0d3cb8f161271ab17.webm?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2082900/extras/98e8c59cc7431eb0d3cb8f161271ab17.mp4?t=1670005419\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Playable in both single-player and split-screen co-op.<br><strong>You need at least one controller to play split-screen co-op.</strong>",
